name: BatuAI - AIC
description:
Another AI character. The TI focuses on the face/upper body. I'm not quite happy how he adapts to clothing. I might do another run with different input images to improve the model.

His name is Batu Batbayar. Please use it was dignity and responsibility.

Have fun and give me a review, if you like it.

I'd appreciate it, when you credit this work in your masterpieces.

If you love what I'm creating feel free to buy me a coffee. Good coffee is awesome:

https://www.buymeacoffee.com/donmischo
